==Useful info==
'''Deep elf pyromancers''' are midgame casters that focus on [[fire magic]]. They are commonly found in the mid to late [[Dungeon]], and will also be found roaming the [[Elven Halls]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Like most deep elves, they can inflict impressive damage, but are also rather frail and possess no elemental resistances (not even to fire).
*Even one rank of fire resistance with significantly reduce the threat they pose. Good reason to carry around swap rings like a [[ring of fire]]
*[[Wand of iceblast|Wands of iceblast]] are great at taking out them out along with their summons.

==History==
Deep elf pyromancers were added in [[0.27]] as a [[fire]]-focused, single book version of the [[deep elf mage]].

